cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.AI 

The paper discusses watermarking deep neural networks, which involves both computer security (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The watermarking is applied to image classification models (cs.CV) and the paper proposes a new algorithm that increases the capacity and flexibility of the embedded watermark message (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the robustness of the watermark against model transformation attacks, which is a common concern in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
